Bumps <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop|rubocop> from 1.54.2 to 1.55.0.

Release notes

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/releases|rubocop's releases>._

> *RuboCop 1.55*
> *New features*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/11794|#11794>: Add support to `Style/ArgumentsForwarding` for anonymous arg/kwarg forwarding in Ruby 3.2. (<https://github.com/owst|`@​owst`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12044|#12044>: Make LSP server support `layoutMode` option to run layout cops. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12056|#12056>: Make LSP server support `lintMode` option to run lint cops. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12046|#12046>: Make `ReturnNilInPredicateMethodDefinition` aware of `nil` at the end of predicate method definition. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> 
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12055|#12055>: Allow parentheses in single-line match patterns when using the `omit_parentheses` style of `Style/MethodCallWithArgsParentheses`. (<https://github.com/gsamokovarov|`@​gsamokovarov`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12050|#12050>: Fix a false positive for `Layout/RedundantLineBreak` when inspecting the `%` form string `%\n\n`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12063|#12063>: Fix `Style/CombinableLoops` when one of the loops is empty. (<https://github.com/fatkodima|`@​fatkodima`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12059|#12059>: Fix a false negative for `Style/StringLiteralsInInterpolation` for symbols with interpolation. (<https://github.com/fatkodima|`@​fatkodima`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/11834|#11834>: Fix false positive for when variable in inside conditional branch in nested node. (<https://github.com/alexeyschepin|`@​alexeyschepin`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/11802|#11802>: Improve handling of `[]` and `()` with percent symbol arrays. (<https://github.com/jasondoc3|`@​jasondoc3`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12052|#12052>: Fix "Subfolders can't include glob special characters". (<https://github.com/meric426|`@​meric426`>, <https://github.com/loveo|`@​loveo`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12062|#12062>: Fix `LoadError` when loading RuboCop from a symlinked location on Windows. (<https://github.com/p0deje|`@​p0deje`>)
> 
> *Changes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12064|#12064>: Make `Style/RedundantArgument` aware of `exit` and `exit!`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12015|#12015>: Mark `Style/HashConversion` as unsafe autocorrection. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)

Changelog

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md|rubocop's changelog>._

> *1.55.0 (2023-07-25)*
> *New features*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/11794|#11794>: Add support to `Style/ArgumentsForwarding` for anonymous arg/kwarg forwarding in Ruby 3.2. ([<https://github.com/owst|`@​owst`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12044|#12044>: Make LSP server support `layoutMode` option to run layout cops. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12056|#12056>: Make LSP server support `lintMode` option to run lint cops. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12046|#12046>: Make `ReturnNilInPredicateMethodDefinition` aware of `nil` at the end of predicate method definition. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> 
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12055|#12055>: Allow parentheses in single-line match patterns when using the `omit_parentheses` style of `Style/MethodCallWithArgsParentheses`. ([<https://github.com/gsamokovarov|`@​gsamokovarov`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12050|#12050>: Fix a false positive for `Layout/RedundantLineBreak` when inspecting the `%` form string `%\n\n`. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12063|#12063>: Fix `Style/CombinableLoops` when one of the loops is empty. ([<https://github.com/fatkodima|`@​fatkodima`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12059|#12059>: Fix a false negative for `Style/StringLiteralsInInterpolation` for symbols with interpolation. ([<https://github.com/fatkodima|`@​fatkodima`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/11834|#11834>: Fix false positive for when variable in inside conditional branch in nested node. ([<https://github.com/alexeyschepin|`@​alexeyschepin`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/11802|#11802>: Improve handling of `[]` and `()` with percent symbol arrays. ([<https://github.com/jasondoc3|`@​jasondoc3`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12052|#12052>: Fix "Subfolders can't include glob special characters". ([<https://github.com/meric426|`@​meric426`>][], [<https://github.com/loveo|`@​loveo`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12062|#12062>: Fix `LoadError` when loading RuboCop from a symlinked location on Windows. ([<https://github.com/p0deje|`@​p0deje`>][])
> 
> *Changes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12064|#12064>: Make `Style/RedundantArgument` aware of `exit` and `exit!`. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12015|#12015>: Mark `Style/HashConversion` as unsafe autocorrection. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])

• <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/commit/9bc0064008f69533e25f4d7c375898c1121f6652|`9bc0064`> Make `Style/RedundantArgument` aware of `exit` and `exit!`
